"\"<p data-start=\\\"228\\\" data-end=\\\"532\\\">In today\u2019s fast-paced and high-pressure work environments, employee well-being is no longer a \u201cnice-to-have\u201d\u2014it\u2019s a strategic priority. This engaging and practical workshop is designed to help leaders, people managers, and HR professionals understand the powerful link between well-being and performance.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"228\\\" data-end=\\\"532\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"534\\\" data-end=\\\"878\\\">Participants will gain insights into the key drivers of employee happiness, including psychological safety, work-life balance, emotional intelligence, and workplace culture. The session provides actionable tools to identify signs of burnout, reduce stress, and implement supportive practices that promote mental, emotional, and social wellness.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"534\\\" data-end=\\\"878\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"880\\\" data-end=\\\"1084\\\"><em data-start=\\\"880\\\" data-end=\\\"910\\\">Happy Teams, Healthy Results<\/em> empowers organizations to build healthier workplaces\u2014where people thrive, collaboration grows, and business outcomes improve. Because when employees feel well, they do well.<\/p>\""